OL,3,CThe Lancastria: What happened and why
OL,4,Cis the tragedy 'forgotten'?
OL,6,FThis year marks 85 years since
OL,7,FBritain's worst maritime disaster -
OL,8,Fbut little is know about the wartime
OL,9,Fsinking of the Lancastria in 1940.
OL,11,FIt is estimated between 4,000 and
OL,12,F7,000 people died when a rescue
OL,13,Fmission for British troops went wrong.
OL,15,FWhat was the Lancastria?
