OL,3,CThe Lancastria: What happened and why
OL,4,Cis the tragedy 'forgotten'?
OL,6,FShe made a number of sailings during
OL,7,Fthe War after being refitted in
OL,8,FLiverpool, before, in June 1940, she
OL,9,Fwas sent to the French port of Saint-
OL,10,FNazaire to help with evacuating
OL,11,FBritish nationals and troops.
OL,13,FITV Granada Reports correspondent Paul
OL,14,FCrone spoke to relatives of those
OL,15,Fonboard the Lancastria
OL,17,FWhat happened on 17 June 1940?
