OL,3,CThe Lancastria: What happened and why
OL,4,Cis the tragedy 'forgotten'?
OL,6,FThe Lancastria formed part of
OL,7,FOperation Ariel, the effort to
OL,8,Fevacuate British civilians, troops and
OL,9,Fembassy staff from Western France, two
OL,10,Fweeks after the evacuation of Dunkirk.
OL,12,FIt is said that the Captain was
OL,13,Fordered to take as many people as
OL,14,Fpossible on board due to the loss of
OL,15,Fother evacuation vessels, and an
OL,16,Festimated 5000-7000 people were on
OL,17,Fboard despite the ship only being
OL,18,Fbuilt for around 2,500.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
